<!-- §1 VOCAB -->
<section data-section="1">
<div class="section-header compare"><h2>Section 1: Key Vocabulary</h2><div class="bilingual">Sección 1: Vocabulario Clave</div></div>
<p class="text-block">Review these terms before you start.</p>
<table class="vocab-table">
<thead><tr><th>Term / Término</th><th>Definition / Definición</th><th>Example / Ejemplo</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td><strong>Loop</strong><br><span class="es">Bucle</span></td><td>Code that repeats.<br><span class="es">Código que se repite.</span></td><td><code>for i in range(5):</code></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Iteration</strong><br><span class="es">Iteración</span></td><td>One single pass through the loop body.<br><span class="es">Una pasada por el cuerpo del bucle.</span></td><td>5 iterations = runs 5 times</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Condition</strong><br><span class="es">Condición</span></td><td>A test: <code>True</code> or <code>False</code>.<br><span class="es">Verdadero o falso.</span></td><td><code>x &lt; 10</code></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Counter variable</strong><br><span class="es">Variable contador</span></td><td>Tracks loop iterations.<br><span class="es">Registra las iteraciones.</span></td><td><code>i</code> in <code>for i in range(5)</code></td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Infinite loop</strong><br><span class="es">Bucle infinito</span></td><td>A loop that never stops.<br><span class="es">Un bucle que nunca para.</span></td><td>Forgetting to update the counter</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong><code>range()</code></strong></td><td>Generates a number sequence.<br><span class="es">Genera una secuencia.</span></td><td><code>range(0, 10, 2)</code> → 0,2,4,6,8</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
</section>
<hr class="divider">

<!-- §2 WHILE LOOP -->
<section data-section="2">
<div class="section-header while"><h2>Section 2: Meet the <code>while</code> Loop</h2><div class="bilingual">Sección 2: Conoce el Bucle while</div></div>
<p class="text-block">A <code>while</code> loop keeps running <strong>as long as a condition is True</strong>.</p>
<p class="text-block es">Un bucle while sigue corriendo mientras una condición sea verdadera.</p>
<div class="callout" data-icon="💡"><div class="callout-title">Pattern / Patrón</div>
<p class="text-block" style="margin:0">Every <code>while</code> loop needs: (1) starting value, (2) condition, (3) update. Forget #3 → infinite loop.</p></div>

<div class="checkpoint">✏️ Trace 1 of 6</div>
<p class="text-block"><strong>Read first. Do NOT run yet.</strong></p>
<div class="code-label">📋 Code Block A <span class="copy-hint">Read → Predict → Run</span></div>
<div class="code-display"><div><span class="ln">1</span><span class="var">count</span> = <span class="num">1</span></div><div><span class="ln">2</span><span class="kw">while</span> <span class="var">count</span> &lt;= <span class="num">5</span>:</div><div><span class="ln">3</span>    <span class="fn">print</span>(<span class="var">count</span>)</div><div><span class="ln">4</span>    <span class="var">count</span> = <span class="var">count</span> + <span class="num">1</span></div></div>
<div class="predict-box"><div class="predict-label">🔮 PREDICT: What will this print?</div><div class="predict-sub">PREDICE — Write your prediction BEFORE running.</div><textarea placeholder="Write each output value..."></textarea></div>

<div class="trinket-wrapper">
  <div class="trinket-label"><span class="trinket-dot"></span> Run it / Córrelo — Code Block A</div>
  <!-- ⚠️ TEACHER: Replace the src URL below with your Trinket embed URL for Code Block A -->
  <!-- Create at trinket.io/python3 → paste the code → Share → Embed → copy the URL -->
<iframe src="https://trinket.io/embed/python/2548e63d83ba" width="100%" height="600" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  <div class="trinket-setup">Trinket setup: count = 1 → while count <= 5: print(count), count = count + 1</div>
</div>
<div class="reveal-section"><button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleReveal(this)">Show explanation / Mostrar explicación</button><div class="reveal-content"><p><strong>Output:</strong> 1, 2, 3, 4, 5</p><p>count starts at 1. Each pass: print, add 1. At 6, <code>6 &lt;= 5</code> is False → stops.</p><p class="es">count empieza en 1. Cuando llega a 6, la condición es falsa → para.</p></div></div>

<div class="checkpoint">✏️ Trace 2 of 6</div>
<div class="code-label">📋 Code Block B</div>
<div class="code-display"><div><span class="ln">1</span><span class="var">x</span> = <span class="num">10</span></div><div><span class="ln">2</span><span class="kw">while</span> <span class="var">x</span> > <span class="num">0</span>:</div><div><span class="ln">3</span>    <span class="fn">print</span>(<span class="var">x</span>)</div><div><span class="ln">4</span>    <span class="var">x</span> = <span class="var">x</span> - <span class="num">3</span></div></div>
<div class="predict-box"><div class="predict-label">🔮 PREDICT: What numbers will print?</div><textarea placeholder="List each number..."></textarea></div>

<div class="trinket-wrapper">
  <div class="trinket-label"><span class="trinket-dot"></span> Run it / Córrelo — Code Block B</div>
