<iframe src="https://trinket.io/embed/python/4021566a90cd" width="100%" height="600" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  <div class="trinket-setup">Trinket setup: x = 10 → while x > 0: print(x), x = x - 3</div>
</div>
<div class="reveal-section"><button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleReveal(this)">Show explanation / Mostrar explicación</button><div class="reveal-content"><p><strong>Output:</strong> 10, 7, 4, 1</p><p>Trace: 10→7→4→1→-2. At -2, condition is False.</p></div></div>
</section>
<hr class="divider">

<!-- §3 FOR LOOP -->
<section data-section="3">
<div class="section-header for"><h2>Section 3: Meet the <code>for</code> Loop</h2><div class="bilingual">Sección 3: Conoce el Bucle for</div></div>
<p class="text-block">A <code>for</code> loop runs a <strong>specific number of times</strong>. <code>range()</code> controls start, stop, step.</p>
<div class="callout" data-icon="📐"><div class="callout-title">range() Cheat Sheet</div>
<p class="text-block" style="margin:0"><code>range(5)</code> → 0,1,2,3,4<br><code>range(2,8)</code> → 2,3,4,5,6,7<br><code>range(0,20,5)</code> → 0,5,10,15<br><code>range(10,0,-2)</code> → 10,8,6,4,2</p></div>

<div class="checkpoint">✏️ Trace 3 of 6</div>
<div class="code-label">📋 Code Block C</div>
<div class="code-display"><div><span class="ln">1</span><span class="kw">for</span> <span class="var">i</span> <span class="kw">in</span> <span class="fn">range</span>(<span class="num">5</span>):</div><div><span class="ln">2</span>    <span class="fn">print</span>(<span class="var">i</span>)</div></div>
<div class="predict-box"><div class="predict-label">🔮 PREDICT: What prints? How many lines?</div><textarea placeholder="Your prediction..."></textarea></div>

<div class="trinket-wrapper">
  <div class="trinket-label"><span class="trinket-dot"></span> Run it / Córrelo — Code Block C</div>
  <!-- ⚠️ TEACHER: Replace the src URL below with your Trinket embed URL for Code Block C -->
  <!-- Create at trinket.io/python3 → paste the code → Share → Embed → copy the URL -->
<iframe src="https://trinket.io/embed/python/d7c1116c131e" width="100%" height="600" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  <div class="trinket-setup">Trinket setup: for i in range(5): print(i)</div>
</div>
<div class="reveal-section"><button class="reveal-btn" onclick="toggleReveal(this)">Show explanation / Mostrar explicación</button><div class="reveal-content"><p><strong>Output:</strong> 0,1,2,3,4 (5 lines). range(5) stops <em>before</em> 5.</p></div></div>

<div class="checkpoint">✏️ Trace 4 of 6</div>
<div class="code-label">📋 Code Block D</div>
<div class="code-display"><div><span class="ln">1</span><span class="kw">for</span> <span class="var">i</span> <span class="kw">in</span> <span class="fn">range</span>(<span class="num">10</span>, <span class="num">101</span>, <span class="num">10</span>):</div><div><span class="ln">2</span>    <span class="fn">print</span>(<span class="var">i</span>)</div></div>
<div class="predict-box"><div class="predict-label">🔮 PREDICT: First number? Last?</div><textarea placeholder="First: ___ Last: ___"></textarea></div>

<div class="trinket-wrapper">
  <div class="trinket-label"><span class="trinket-dot"></span> Run it / Córrelo — Code Block D</div>
  <!-- ⚠️ TEACHER: Replace the src URL below with your Trinket embed URL for Code Block D -->
