<!-- §4 SIDE-BY-SIDE -->
<section data-section="4">
<div class="section-header compare"><h2>Section 4: Same Output, Two Loops</h2><div class="bilingual">Sección 4: Misma Salida, Dos Bucles</div></div>
<div class="comparison">
<div class="col while-col"><h3>while version</h3><div class="code-display" style="border:none;margin:0;padding:.8rem"><div><span class="var">i</span> = <span class="num">0</span></div><div><span class="kw">while</span> <span class="var">i</span> &lt; <span class="num">5</span>:</div><div>    <span class="fn">print</span>(<span class="var">i</span>)</div><div>    <span class="var">i</span> = <span class="var">i</span> + <span class="num">1</span></div></div></div>
<div class="col for-col"><h3>for version</h3><div class="code-display" style="border:none;margin:0;padding:.8rem"><div><span class="kw">for</span> <span class="var">i</span> <span class="kw">in</span> <span class="fn">range</span>(<span class="num">5</span>):</div><div>    <span class="fn">print</span>(<span class="var">i</span>)</div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="callout" data-icon="🔑"><div class="callout-title">Key Difference / Diferencia Clave</div>
<p class="text-block" style="margin:0"><code>for</code> handles the counter automatically. <code>while</code> requires you to manage all three steps.</p></div>

<p class="text-block">Harder — both count down from 10 to 2 by twos:</p>
<div class="comparison">
