<!-- §5 WHEN TO USE WHICH -->
<section data-section="5">
<div class="section-header compare"><h2>Section 5: When to Use Which?</h2><div class="bilingual">Sección 5: ¿Cuándo Usar Cuál?</div></div>
<div class="comparison">
<div class="col while-col"><h3>Use while when...</h3><p style="font-size:.88rem">You <strong>don't know</strong> how many times. Depends on input or a changing condition.</p><p class="es" style="font-size:.82rem;margin-top:.3rem">Usa while cuando no sabes cuántas veces.</p></div>
<div class="col for-col"><h3>Use for when...</h3><p style="font-size:.88rem">You <strong>know exactly</strong> how many times, or you're counting through a range.</p><p class="es" style="font-size:.82rem;margin-top:.3rem">Usa for cuando sabes exactamente.</p></div>
</div>
</section>
